Xinjiang Goldwind Shares Decline to Record in Hong Kong Trading

-- B y   B i l l y   C h a n
-- 
2011-06-13T05:50:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-13/xinjiang-goldwind-shares-decline-to-record-in-hong-kong-trading.html
Xinjiang Goldwind Science &
Technology Co. fell 7.7 percent to HK$9.10, the lowest level
since its debut in October 2010, in Hong Kong trading as of 1:43
p.m. today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
